size: 18px;\">祈福法会是以礼敬诸佛、忏悔业障、供养三宝，而达到吉祥如意，增福延寿，消灾免难。观世音菩萨是大慈大悲的象征，慈是使他人快乐，悲是帮助他人解脱烦恼和痛苦，慈悲一切、怜悯一切、救护一切众生，就是大慈大悲。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">水神山报国寺，在观世音菩萨出家日这天举行隆重的祈福法会，以此法会功德祈愿天下无灾，大地清宁，众生皆闻佛法，深恩开显智慧，福德圆融！南无大慈大悲观世音菩萨！&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\" title=\"14840597901324.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840597901324.jpg\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"14840597908531.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840597908531.jpg\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\" title=\"14840597906846.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840597906846.jpg\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>','0','0','0',NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'','','','',''),(174,13,0,'【点灯祈福】山西报国寺将举办丁酉新春大型祈福法会',NULL,'admin',1,35,NULL,0,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2017-01-21 18:28:15','报国寺文宣',NULL,'/upload/images/201701/14850545931999.jpg',1,1,'报国寺定于2017年1月27日至2月11日（农历腊月三十至正月十五）隆重举行丁酉新春大型祈福法会，法会期间各位信善可以为自己、家人、朋友在天王殿、大文殊殿、大雄宝殿点灯笼，祈福。',0,'<p style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><img title=\"14850779688706.jpg\" alt=\"灯.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14850779688706.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">一灯能破千年暗。灯代表着光明和智慧，是佛教的十种供养之一，如《菩萨藏经》所言：<span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;\">“</span>百千灯明忏悔罪”，《无量寿经》所述，<span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;\">”</span>为世灯明最福田”，在佛前供灯，培福消业，利益众生，也象征着佛光普照，法脉不息。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 17px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">《佛为首迦长者说业报差别经》里曾宣讲了供灯的十种功德：</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">一、照世如灯。二、肉眼不坏。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">三、得于天眼。四、善恶智能。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">五、灭除大暗。 六、得智能明。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">七、不在暗处。 八、具大福报。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">九、命终生天。 十、速证涅槃。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><img title=\"14852479662286.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14852479662286.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 17px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">挂灯笼的习俗也与礼佛的仪轨有关。据《僧史略》载，佛祖释迦牟尼示现神变、降伏神魔于正月十五日，为纪念佛祖神变，此日需举行燃灯法会。东汉明帝因梦而向西求法，佛法由此东来，曾敕令正月十五佛祖神变之日燃灯，并亲自到寺院张灯，以示礼佛，后演变为民间盛大节日。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 17px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">农历新年到来之际，山西报国寺定于<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">2017</span>年<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">1</span>月<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">27</span>日至<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">2</span>月<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">11</span>日（农历腊月三十至正月十五）隆重举行丁酉新春大型诵经祈福法会。本次法会期间，寺院将在天王殿、大文殊殿、大雄宝殿挂灯笼，信众可点灯为自己和家人朋友等亲属祈福，心灯种类有，财源广进灯、学业智慧灯、平安吉祥灯。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 17px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">随喜供灯功德，阿弥陀佛</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 14px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 17px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">寺院地址：山西盂县北山神（离高铁阳泉北站约<span sty