images/201701/20170107230939943994.jpg',1,1,'农历腊月初八（公历2017年1月5日）欣逢释迦牟尼佛成道日，报国寺举行斋天、祈福等诸多佛事及施粥活动。',200,'<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">农历腊月初八（公历2017年1月5日）欣逢释迦牟尼佛成道日，报国寺举行斋天、祈福等诸多佛事及施粥活动。纪念这个殊胜的节日，意在不忘佛祖誓成佛道而代众生所受的苦难，不忘法轮未转，食轮先转，牧女为助太子成道所做的供养，同时也感恩四众弟子对道场的护持。感恩十方信众对三宝的护持，愿三宝加持护佑众生离苦得乐。并祈愿风调雨顺、世界和平、国泰民安！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 18px;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img title=\"14840530932899.jpg\" alt=\"20170107230939943994.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840530932899.jpg\"/>&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img title=\"14840531126062.jpg\" alt=\"20170107230926522652.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840531126062.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img title=\"14840533958283.jpg\" alt=\"20170107230985618561.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840533958283.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img title=\"14840534197952.jpg\" alt=\"20170107230960566056.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840534197952.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img title=\"14840534746062.jpg\" alt=\"20170107230974327432.jpg\" src=\"/upload/images/201701/14840534746062.jpg\"/></span></p>','0','0','0',NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'','','','',''),(38,13,0,'报国寺举行祈福放生法会','放生法会','admin',1,13,NULL,0,0,'',0,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,2107,'201