&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">《妙法莲华经》称为经中之王。素有“开悟的楞严，成佛的法华”之赞誉。法华偈云：“六万余言七轴装，无边妙义广含藏；白玉齿边流舍利，红莲舌上放毫光；喉中甘露涓涓润，口中醍醐滴滴凉；假饶造罪过山狱，不须妙法两三行。”历代以来，以修持《妙法莲华经》者，也不可胜记，且持验无比。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">《妙法莲华经》主要阐述佛陀在法华会上，开权显实，直畅本怀。故经云：“诸佛世尊唯一大事因缘故，出现于世……欲令众生开示悟入佛之知见。”《妙法莲华经》之妙，妙在甚深法门、希有难信；妙在只要恭敬礼拜、合掌乃至举一手、或小低头，以此善根功德，将来都能成佛。故经云：“或有人礼拜，或复但合掌，乃至举一手、或复小低头，以此供养像，渐见无量佛，自成无上道，广度无数众，入无余涅槃，如薪尽火灭。若人散乱心，入于塔庙中，一称南无佛，皆已成佛道。”&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">愿广大信众通过法会，同沾法喜，共沐祯祥，将此功德回施施主自身，冀希自己及家属得以消灾免难、增福延寿、平安健康、合家幸福；也普令广大信众，广种善根，培植福慧，心开意解，得法水滋润，共成佛道，因此功德最为殊胜！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;,